  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cross-sectional, one visit study. All the data will be collected through questionnaires.
      Descriptives statistics will be applied to the data. 832 patients will participate to the
      study and 104 physicians.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
